title: Setting Yourself Up for Financial Success (Hour 2)
description:
George Kamel & Kristina Ellis discuss:

Paying off debt with a tight budget,

Cashing out an IRA,

Setting yourself up for financial success,

Getting a spouse on board with the baby steps,

Avoiding online dating scams,

Quitting a job to go back to school.


Support Our Sponsor:
PODS Moving & Storage
